jason.bb
Class ChainBB

java.lang.Object
  jason.bb.ChainBBAdapter
      jason.bb.ChainBB
All Implemented Interfaces:
BeliefBase, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Literal>
public class ChainBB
extends ChainBBAdapter

A wrapper for a chain of belief bases customisations. The arguments are the belief bases in the chain jason.bb.ChainBB( bb1, bb2, bb3, ... ) where each BB is bbclass(bb paramters) e.g.: 

  agents:
        bob beliefBaseClass jason.bb.ChainBB(
              jason.bb.TextPersistentBB,
              jason.bb.IndexedBB("student(key,_)", "depot(_,_,_)")
            );
